cs.CR, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.AR, cs.SY 

This paper deals with memory safety checkers and techniques for eliminating redundant bounds checking. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also proposes a model-based inference approach, which could potentially fall under the categories of robotics (cs.RO) or systems and control (cs.SY).
